#Package: icewm-experimental
#Architecture: any
#Depends: icewm-common (= ${Source-Version}), icewm-gnome-support (= ${Source-Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}
#Recommends: gnome-core
#Provides: x-window-manager
#Description: wonderful Win95-OS/2-Motif-like window manager
# Window Manager for X Window System. Can emulate the look of Windows'95,
# OS/2 Warp 3,4, Motif. Tries to take the best features of the above systems.
# Features multiple workspaces, opaque move/resize, task bar, window list,
# mailbox status, digital clock. Fast and small.
# .
# This is the experimental version of IceWM. It contains some additional
# experimental features, including antialiasing of icons, support for
# sound events and gradients.
# .
# GNOME support files can be found in the `icewm-gnome-support' package.
# .
# Extra themes are available from the icewm-themes package.
